Rating, 5 stars,  · February 2023,  · Stayed over a week
rating_comment: Very good area to stay kind people all around. Local bangladeshi food resturant downstairs and it is close to the airport where tons of people come to visit to see the planes. It will take you 30 taka from jashmuddin pakar matha to badaldi. King bed is a big plus. Decent price as well. Kawsar and manager will help you if you need anything. Defenit recommended

info: Rating, 5 stars,  · December 2022,  · Stayed over a week
rating_comment: Kawsar is a very good guest. He fixed any issues I had. The place is located behind the airport and there is decent local stores all around. However online food panda and food delivery does not come here. The room consists of a king bed which is very good and people around is very nice. If you want to experience a good feel of Dhaka without all the high rise buildings this might be a good place for you. I would recommend this to anyone. Thanks
